data.description: THIS IS YOUR OPPORTUNITY CALLING! It's a great single story with an open concept and priced right! A SPACIOUS living area will be perfect for entertaining. There is plenty of space in the kitchen, which is ideal for cooking many delicious meals. The main Bedroom is on the opposite side of the house from the other 2 bedrooms to give you more privacy! This home is close to Beal Air Force Base, Toyota Amphitheater, and Feather River. The spacious main bedroom has room for a king-size bed and chairs or a sitting area. Inside laundry and has a 3-car garage. Spacious back and side yards in almost a quarter-acre lot. There is plenty of room to do many things in the backyard. The large side yard has the potential for RV parking. There is certainly plenty of room for a BBQ party in the summertime. Do Not Pass Up This Perfect Opportunity To Be A Homeowner.
